      "side": 1,
      "message": "If you take Matt\u0027s suggestion and have the default behavior be dump all chassis, then perhaps this becomes an option with no argument?\n\nThen there is a separate option (-c or -n or something) for the \"chassis number\"?\n\nRegardless, you need to specify in the command help that the user should specify a chassis number from 1 to N, where N is the number of chassis.",
